Description: Fast native text editor with GPU rendering
 NotepadX is a Rust-built text editor focused on making everyday editing
 feel immediate, even on large files, without shipping a browser runtime.
 .
 Features include GPU-accelerated text rendering via wgpu, rope-based buffer
 for scalable editing, multi-cursor support, find/replace with regex,
 tree-sitter syntax highlighting for 20 languages, session persistence,
 memory-mapped large-file mode with background search, and 20 built-in
 color themes.
